reviews.review:
The game is great. Its a lot of fun. Doesnt matter if you play alone or with friends.
There are also negatives :  
No rewards for playing this game or reach Rank 1;
All cosmetics are in the shop, besides Prestige;
Crushing experiences as Killer if you  play against a 4 man group.

Overall a real fun game with some weaknesses. If they add Emotes i would be happy
